I"Q<ol>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">vi /etc/vmware/esx.conf</code></li>
  <li>Find <code class="highlighter-rouge">/device/&lt;$PCI_ID&gt;/owner = "passthru"</code>.</li>
  <li>Replace <code class="highlighter-rouge">passthru</code> with <code class="highlighter-rouge">vmkernel</code>.</li>
  <li>Reboot ESXi.</li>
</ol>

